(107, 1, '2023-02-16 18:04:51', '2023-02-16 18:04:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Html code is the basic building block of web development for beginners it becomes difficult to learn it by themself. Here is a complete list of HTML code examples with syntax and how to use this code or tags in HTML.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML code for the button with link</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I you want to use the button with a link then you can use a hyperlink tag to create a button with CSS or you can put your button under &lt;a&gt; tag </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;button class=\"btn\"&gt;click me&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;a href=\"btn\"&gt;click me&lt;/a&gt;\n\n&lt;style&gt;\n.btn{\n outline:none;  //toremove default ouline from button\n border:none;   // to remove border\n text-decoration:none;\n }\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML code for the video </h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can use the video tag of html5 to embed video in your HTML page or webpage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;video width=\"320\" height=\"240\" controls&gt;\n  &lt;source src=\"movie.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"&gt;  //video type and source \n  &lt;source src=\"movie.ogg\" type=\"video/ogg\"&gt;  //aletrnate video type with source\n\n&lt;/video&gt;</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML code for the table</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>to show tabular data you will have to use the table tag of HTML. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\ntable {\n  font-family: arial, sans-serif;\n  border-collapse: collapse;\n  width: 100%;\n}\n\ntr:nth-child(even) {\n  background-color: #dddddd;\n}\ntd, th {\n  border: 1px solid #dddddd;\n  text-align: left;\n  padding: 8px;\n}\n&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n\n&lt;h2&gt;HTML Table&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;table&gt;\n  &lt;tr&gt;\n    &lt;th&gt;Company&lt;/th&gt;\n    &lt;th&gt;Contact&lt;/th&gt;\n    &lt;th&gt;Country&lt;/th&gt;\n  &lt;/tr&gt;\n  &lt;tr&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Alfreds Nodel&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Maria Anders&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Germany&lt;/td&gt;\n  &lt;/tr&gt;\n  &lt;tr&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Centro FF Moctezuma&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Francisco Chang&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Mexico city&lt;/td&gt;\n  &lt;/tr&gt;\n  &lt;tr&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Ernst Handel&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Roland Tenure&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Austria courty&lt;/td&gt;\n  &lt;/tr&gt;\n  &lt;tr&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Island Trading&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Helen Bennett&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;UK nation&lt;/td&gt;\n  &lt;/tr&gt;\n  &lt;tr&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Laughing Bacchus Winecellars&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Yoshi Tannamuri&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Canada&lt;/td&gt;\n  &lt;/tr&gt;\n  &lt;tr&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Magazzini Alimentari Riuniti&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Giovanni Rovelli&lt;/td&gt;\n    &lt;td&gt;Italy&lt;/td&gt;\n  &lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;\n\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n\n</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML code for Registration form</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For the HTML code of registration. You will need to use of form tag and inputs to enter the information like email name mobile number etc. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe height=\"300\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Simple Registration Form\" src=\"https://codepen.io/debbsefe/embed/povBzrG?default-tab=html%2Cresult\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/debbsefe/pen/povBzrG\">\n  Simple Registration Form</a> by eferha  (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/debbsefe\">@debbsefe</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML code for login page</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For the HTML code of the login page, you can use the same code as the registration page. The only thing you need to change is the title of the page and submit function which you want to perform on submit of the login form.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe height=\"300\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Login Page Invite only mode\" src=\"https://codepen.io/wellnesswonders/embed/WNgbEBx?default-tab=html%2Cresult\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/wellnesswonders/pen/WNgbEBx\">\n  Login Page Invite only mode</a> by Maxbill (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/wellnesswonders\">@wellnesswonders</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML code for the form</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The HTML form is the most important element of website design and web development as most of the frontend web pages need this tag if you are designing a login or registration page of another dashboard page.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;form action=\"/action.php\"&gt;\n  &lt;label for=\"firstname\"&gt;First name:&lt;/label&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n  &lt;input type=\"text\" id=\"firstname\" name=\"fname\" value=\"John\"&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n  &lt;label for=\"lname\"&gt;Last name:&lt;/label&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n  &lt;input type=\"text\" id=\"lastname\" name=\"lname\" value=\"Doe\"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n  &lt;input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\"&gt;\n&lt;/form&gt; </code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML form examples with code</h2>\