frame animation of css3 </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe height=\"300\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"CSS Blinking Text\" src=\"https://codepen.io/engza/embed/VGYeEx?default-tab=html%2Cresult\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/engza/pen/VGYeEx\">\n  CSS Blinking Text</a> by Zach (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/engza\">@engza</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML code for link open in new tab</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To open and webpage using a hyperlink tag you can add the target attribute to open the webpage or HTML in a new tab.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;a href=\"https://frontendzone.com\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;open page&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>HTML code for gradient background</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>top 5 Best gradient background with CSS and HTML</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe height=\"400\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Gradient Background Animation\" src=\"https://codepen.io/emr3rden/embed/eYVOBRY?default-tab=html%2Cresult\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/emr3rden/pen/eYVOBRY\">\n  Gradient Background Animation</a> by Emre Erden (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/emr3rden\">@emr3rden</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe height=\"400\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Simple Footer\" src=\"https://codepen.io/baahubali92/embed/qGWYXO?default-tab=html%2Cresult\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/baahubali92/pen/qGWYXO\">\n  Simple Footer</a> by Baahubali (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/baahubali92\">@baahubali92</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'HTML code example', 'HTML code example for login page , registration page , form and many more with html and css', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'html-code-example', '', '', '2023-02-16 18:13:54', '2023-02-16 18:13:54', '', 0, 'https://cms.frontendzone.com/?p=107', 0, 'post', '', 0),
