(252, 1, '2023-03-30 17:12:54', '2023-03-30 17:12:54', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HTML and CSS are basic technologies that are important to design any website or web application. If you are starting to design a website or web application HTML and CSS are the first things that you will need to design a website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now, if you were searching to build a real-world website with HTML and CSS you will definitely be a beginner in web development don\'t worry, I am going to tell you everything about how you can build a real-world website with HTML and CSS.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It will be very good if you have vs code installed or if you are already using it. It will make your work faster to write code.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Step-by-step process to build a website with HTML &amp; CSS</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>follow steps by steps process on how to design a real word website in HTML and CSS easily.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Step 1: Create a folder name \"website\"</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Create a folder name as a website and open this folder in vs code.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":253,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://cms.frontendzone.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/how-to-build-a-real-world-website-in-html-and-css-1024x640.png\" alt=\"build responsive real-world websites with html and css\" class=\"wp-image-253\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Step 2: Create index.html and main.css files in the website folder</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now you have to write your HTML code in the index.html file and write your CSS code in the main.css file. Create a folder image also named images.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":255,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://cms.frontendzone.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Screenshot-118-1024x640.png\" alt=\"build responsive real-world websites with html and css\" class=\"wp-image-255\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Step 3: Start designing your website in HTML&amp; CSS</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now your folder structure is ready and you are good to go now with the designing step to design your website in HTML and CSS.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These were the basic setup for your html &amp; css websites. Now think about what type of design and sections you want in your website and start adding HTML code for your website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {\"id\":256,\"href\":\"https://cms.frontendzone.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/real-world-website-design-with-html-and-css.pdf\",\"displayPreview\":true} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><object class=\"wp-block-file__embed\" data=\"https://cms.frontendzone.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/real-world-website-design-with-html-and-css.pdf\" type=\"application/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"real-world-website-design-with-html-and-css\"></object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-c007f732-8b0a-49ca-96a7-c2a5eb5f0d64\" href=\"https://cms.frontendzone.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/real-world-website-design-with-html-and-css.pdf\">real-world-website-design-with-html-and-css</a><a href=\"https://cms.frontendzone.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/real-world-website-design-with-html-and-css.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button wp-element-button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-c007f732-8b0a-49ca-96a7-c2a5eb5f0d64\">build responsive real-world websites with HTML and CSS</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n