wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://www.pureflix.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.pureflix.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Pure flix</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://upfaithandfamily.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://upfaithandfamily.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Up Faith &amp; Family</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://cf.crossflixplus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://cf.crossflixplus.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Crossflix+</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"http://dovechannel.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"http://dovechannel.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Dove Channel</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Reasons behind why is Netflix removing Christian movies</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have already talked in brief about why is Netflix removing Christian movies. Now let\'s discuss in detail every reason for removing Christian movies from Netflix.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Licensing agreements</strong> - There may be a licensing issue behind removing Christian content from Netflix. that\'s why Netflix is not removing all the Christian movies it may try to remove movies that may not have proper license</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Content Strategy</strong> - Netflix may also have a plan to change content genres and user demand.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong> Movies affecting faith</strong> - Some of the movies that may conflict with people\'s faith Netflix may make </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>decisions to remove those movies from its platform. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>content rotation</strong> - streaming platform regularly update their content to make user experience fresh and variety of options to the subscribers and this roatation may affects removal of such movies which have been old or less watched.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Content quality and relevance</strong> - Every streaming platform strive to maintain high quality of content  to make their user engaged and loved. and if movies are outdatedor not meeting qaulity standard for the platform they removed such movies. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":416,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://cms.frontendzone.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/reasons-behind-removal-of-christian-movies-from-netflix.png\" alt=\"reasons-behind-removal-of-christian-movies-from-netflix\" class=\"wp-image-416\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Movies Removed by Netflix</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some of the movies which were based on faith </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Arrows</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The Healer</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li> The Gospel of Matthew</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li> Soul Surfer, Freshman Year</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The Young Messiah</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In conclusion  💁‍♀️ , The news and rumor that netflix is going to remove christian movies from its plaform is not true.Social media posts in March 2021 were claiming that Netflix has removed or was planning to remove all Christian movies from its streaming platform. No ,<strong>Netflix has not been removing Christian movies in fact it filters out some christian movies to make them available freely. </strong>You still can enjoy the cristian movies on netflix. You can <strong>comment</strong> your view on this rumor <strong>Thanks for reading.</strong> 😇</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>List of some top Christian movies on Netflix</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here in this video, you can find the most famous Christian movies on Netflix that every Christian must watch.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"405\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bXUrK0KiNX0?si=dWTpoL4-_UAfxhsl\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Playlist of 200 Christian movies on Netflix</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"405\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?si=XrgtQzcIpH8TPpDF&amp;list=PL88wQRqoc0IntBERnAFx5XRgNUIHo3XQS\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Why is Netflix removing Christian movies ? Truth or rumour 😲', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-is-netflix-removing-christian-movies', '', '', '2023-09-09 20:32:19', '2023-09-09 20:32:19', '', 0, 'https://cms.frontendzone.com/?p=408', 0, 'post', '', 0),
