onsive real-world websites with html and css</strong></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Simple Registration form in HTML with CSS source code</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Document</title>\n    <style>\n        *{transition: all 0.3s;}\n        form.myform{\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            width: 400px;\n            max-width:100%;\n            background: #f2eaea;\n            padding:60px 30px;\n            font-family: sans-serif;\n        }\n       .myform input{\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            outline: none;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 2px solid #ddd;\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n       .myform input:invalid{color: red;}\n       .myform input:valid{color: rgb(12, 203, 123);}\n       .myform input:focus{\n            border-color: blue;\n        }\n        .myform button{\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            background: teal;\n            color: #fff;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            outline: none;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n      \n    </style>\n\n\n    <form class=\"myform\">\n        <h2>Register Now</h2>\n        <input required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"First Name\">\n        <input required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Last Name\">\n        <input required=\"\" minlength=\"10\" maxlength=\"12\" type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"Mobile\">\n        <input required=\"\" type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email\">\n        <input required=\"\" type=\"password\" placeholder=\"Password\">\n        <button type=\"submit\">Register</button>\n    </form>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<a class=\"theme-btn download-btn\" title=\"registration form in HTML with CSS source code\" id=\"download-registration-html\" href=\"/demo/registration-form.htm